cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a novel segmentation approach for joint optic disc and cup segmentation using deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions the use of CNNs, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with medical imaging, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
